"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-intimacy-ban-sex-olympic-village-paris-games-2024\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News August 3, 2024 / 10:00 AM EDT/ CBS News What happens in the Olympic village may stay in the Olympic village, but how does a setting that's known fora lively hookup cultureimpact athletes' performances?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9998579957639205, \"rank\": 0.00014129084853874827, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9998579957639205, \"rank\": 0.00014129084853874827, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"fora lively hookup cultureimpact athletes' performances\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the2024 Gamesheat up in Paris, we asked experts what theintimacy ban lift, which was set in place during the2020 Tokyo gamesbecause of theCOVID pandemic, might mean for this year's event.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999981173005032, \"rank\": 1.88273494648767e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9982977468972768, \"rank\": 0.0012963528358672888, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"what theintimacy ban lift\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"the2020\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"theCOVID pandemic\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's event\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex does not seem to have any positive or negative impact on people's physical capacities, sociologist and relationship expertJennifer Gunsaullustold CBS News - but, there are a few related things that could affect performance, including hookup culture itself.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9998579957639205, \"rank\": 0.00014129084853874827, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sex\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"any positive or negative impact\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"people's physical capacities\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"sociologist\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"relationship\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"a few related things\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"hookup culture\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the Olympic Village, it's so much around the hookup scene, which often involves staying up later, getting less sleep, drinking and partying \\u2026 things like that.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 682, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 5.179414647489797e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hookup scene\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"less sleep\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So in terms of the physical aspects, those seem to be the biggest issues,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"the physical aspects\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest issues\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly, things likesleepand alcohol can definitely have an impact on your physical performance, a negative impact.\\\"\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 960}, {\"ngram\": \"an impact\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"your physical performance\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"a negative impact\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1038}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are also some psychological considerations around sex.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some psychological considerations\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, sex can also release endorphins, which can have an impact on our mood and energy, saidJoy Berkheimer, a sexologist and licensed marriage and family therapist.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"endorphins\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"an impact\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"our mood\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"saidJoy Berkheimer\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"a sexologist\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"marriage and family therapist\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While this will not give you super strength or speed - a.k.a., physiological impacts - it could elevate mood and reduce worry.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"super strength\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"speed - a.k.a., physiological impacts\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"mood\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"worry\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It may not make (performance) better, but it may remove mental blocks - the fear of not being able to do a thing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"mental blocks\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"the fear\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"a thing\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The feedback you receive from a partner on your sexual performance can also make a mental mark - both good or bad.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The feedback\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"a partner\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"your sexual performance\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"a mental mark\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Someone is still expressing to you your capacity for doing things,\\\" Berkheimer said.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Someone\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"your capacity\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkheimer\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(If) there is a performance failure \\u2026 that could definitely affect you psychologically.\\\"\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a performance failure\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How a sexual encounter may affect someone all depends on the person, too.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sexual encounter\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your personality, your values, your belief system - all of that,\\\" Berkheimer said, adding, for example, if you have some shame around sex and engage in it, it could affect you differently than someone else.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your values\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"your belief system\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkheimer\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"some shame\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, for athletes who may have been relieved by the previous intimacy ban, potentially renewed social pressure could also create challenges.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous intimacy ban\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"potentially renewed social pressure\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunsaullus agrees everyone is affected differently mentally and emotionally by sex - and especially hooking up, since in comparison, sex with a long-term partner is more likely to be associated with comfort, connection, trust and safety, she said.\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gunsaullus\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term partner\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"comfort\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If (sex with a long-term partner is) part of your routine - connecting and feeling grounded and loved, like that's a great part of your Olympic performance potentially, but hooking up is a whole other crapshoot,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term partner\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"a great part\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"your Olympic performance\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole other crapshoot\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, does it reduce or increase stress for you?\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does it help or hinder your sleep?\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sleep\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does it improve or interfere with your focus?\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your focus\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a small percentage of people who thrive in hookup culture,\\\" she explained, pointing mostly to research on college campuses.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small percentage\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"hookup culture\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"college campuses\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But (for a) majority of people, it's a real up or down.\\\"\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \") majority\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To more fully understand the potential impact of sex on athletes, Berkheimer said more research is needed, especially on women.\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the potential impact\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"sex\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkheimer\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"more research\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What was a little bit disappointing is most of the research was based off of male athletes,\\\" Berkheimer said.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the research\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"male athletes\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"Berkheimer\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I understand there are a lot of male athletes, but I wish there was more research for the experience of a female athlete, because there is so many layers to that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"male athletes\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"more research\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3399}, {\"ngram\": \"a female athlete\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3419}, {\"ngram\": \"so many layers\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Edited byAllison Elyse Gualtieri \\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3487, \"end\": 3496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gualtieri\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gualtieri\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gualtieri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gualtieri\"}, {\"begin\": 3505, \"end\": 3525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(01:23) Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3567}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3603}]}]}"